{"tid":489430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國脫歐談判重大進展 北愛爾蘭實質留在歐盟","createTime":"2017-12-04T16:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-04T22:58:38.000Z","uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5312d8228dc5dae10887277b7c72b9f50e5180","tid":489430,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:13:27.000Z","msg":"英國每日電訊報報導，歐洲理事會主席圖斯克說，在英國脫離歐盟談判中，英國與歐盟已越來越接近就第一階段談判達成協議，可以開始談雙方未來貿易關係。<br />\n<br />\n英國衛報與英國廣播公司報導，英國政府已在愛爾蘭邊界問題上讓步，準備在脫歐後，讓英國北愛爾蘭實質上留在歐盟關稅同盟和單一市場中，以確保北愛爾蘭與愛爾蘭的邊界暢通。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟「英國脫歐談判首席代表」巴尼耶向多名歐洲議會議員透露，英國首相梅伊已同意將北愛爾蘭作為特案處理。消息人士透露，英國與歐盟執委會15頁的共同聲明草稿寫道，英國將透過「法規調整」，讓北愛爾蘭留在歐盟關稅同盟和單一市場。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士說，愛爾蘭將「法規調整」詮釋為讓英國與愛爾蘭雙方享有最高程度的舒適便利。<br />\n<br />\n文翠珊4日在比利時布魯塞爾，與歐洲理事會主席圖斯克、歐盟執委會主席容克、歐盟談判代表巴尼耶共進午餐，希望在14日歐盟峰會前，就第一階段談判談成協議。圖斯克說，他為「談判的進展感到鼓舞」，英國與歐盟在愛爾蘭邊界、分手費與公民權利問題上離達成共識「更接近了」。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟先前表示，在英國脫歐談判中，唯有在公民權利、分手費和北愛爾蘭邊界問題「取得充分進展」，歐盟才願意開始與英國談未來貿易關係。英國希望歐盟同意在14日歐盟峰會上就開始談。<br />\n<br />\n在分手費問題上，據說英國最近同意將費用提高到500億歐元（約台幣1.8兆元）。在歐盟公民權利問題上，據說英國已同意，想在英國定居的300萬歐盟公民，不必付錢取得定居身分。<br />\n<br />\n愛爾蘭希望英國保證，脫歐後不會在彼此邊界上設關卡，而且商品與人員流動仍將保持暢通。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2856180\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F2856180&d=ccqcd2TaKq5pbInitvPWXNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b0fa488d\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/2856180</a>"},{"pid":"1ed5b649fc30b3050cc5487f31380839adf52ff1","tid":489430,"uid":56015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:26:44.000Z","msg":"得北愛實質留歐，咁蘇格蘭之後九成會嘈到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ea33a8036dbdcf02416f32a126d6e122f0c37f","tid":489430,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"UK and EU fail to strike Brexit talks deal<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-42217735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-politics-42217735&d=ccqcd2TaKq5pbInitvPWXNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d6aaef62\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-42217735</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1eb26b857db31638537fc8f3471a7676232cb97","tid":489430,"uid":41452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:33:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/dec/03/may-take-charge-brexit-talks-crucial-brussels-meetings-northern-ireland-border-issue\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fpolitics%2F2017%2Fdec%2F03%2Fmay-take-charge-brexit-talks-crucial-brussels-meetings-northern-ireland-border-issue&d=ccqcd2TaKq5pbInitvPWXNU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=76f11652\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/politics/2017/dec/03/may-take-charge-brexit-talks-crucial-brussels-meetings-northern-ireland-border-issue</a>"},{"pid":"97c0ab31d29812d61918317f8c5443d7c47d6f5b","tid":489430,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T22:58:38.000Z","msg":"睇少啲華霉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本未傾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}